{"tid":1510501,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"中國口岸停查手機　改玩逼拍片賀10.1國慶","createTime":"2019-08-27T08:09:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T04:36:20.000Z","uid":66271,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"56a5a2b52992cd6d2bc6530096e4103d9078d45d","tid":1510501,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T08:09:42.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】內地公安早前為禁止港人把反送中訊息傳至內地，在羅湖及福田等多個口岸加設黑屏風，派出大批人員截查出入境港人手機，情況一度引起港人不安；但有關措施近日突然無聲無息消失，公安再沒大舉截查北上旅客手機，部份黑屏風亦被移走。不過新招卻是層出不窮，有北上港人昨入境東莞時，被公安要求拍宣傳短片，在鏡頭前為十．一國慶說祝賀說話。<br />\n<br />\n早前公安在各口岸截查出入境港人手機，有港人被強迫解開手機密碼鎖，並因手機存有反送中相片及影片，被扣查盤問至少五小時；其間公安甚至追問事主是否反共，並強行收集其10隻手指指模及刺穿其指頭取血液DNA。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a98bda51e8945a25b3e740ff6a5752edcfcfe49","tid":1510501,"uid":1582,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T08:10:02.000Z","msg":"快過呂麗<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"1c8df1b555eb43e6425c65bd523840db18828eaa","tid":1510501,"uid":33930,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T08:10:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bi%2FtobIAPz7vP9zHpdy2ENqg%3D&h=a3ee6df5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bi%2FtobIAPz7vP9zHpdy2ENqg%3D&h=caee3859\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F